{
  "texts": [
    "Because the design was similar to Study 1, we aimed to recruit 400 Englishspeaking participants from Prolific to reappraise six vignettes each across the four conditions.",
    "Four hundred and nine participants completed the task.",
    "We removed three participants from analyses for nonsensical responses, and an additional reappraisal for being unrelated to the vignette.",
    "We also removed two participants for taking extended breaks during the task.",
    "Our final sample included 404 participants (217 female, 185 male, 2 non-binary; age: 𝑀 = 39.69 𝑦𝑒𝑎𝑟𝑠, 𝑆𝐷 = 13.27)."
  ]
}